item.title: I've Completed my PhD at SUTD
item.description:
I’m glad to announce that I’ve completed my PhD in Computer Science with a specialization in Cyber-Physical and Wireless Systems Security at SUTD.

I’ve uploaded my [thesis]() and the [slides]() of my final presentation. For more information have a look [here]()
